There is also artifacts on PAL screens. I've always noted "staircases" in vertical straight lines, and an isolated pixel will randomly have another color than the one it's supposed to. If it scrolls, then it will flickers among multiple colors. A good example of this is the eye on the statues at the entrance of Castlevania.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Tue Dec 20, 2011 3:26 pm</p><hr />
